content: Once they've been defeated, look for some stairs left of the lantern decorations, and head to the lower level. There's many more green Wisps to absorb, so long as you take out the other Lantern Holder creating more dangerous wisps of his own.

The content is as follows:
Once they've been defeated, look for some stairs left of the lantern decorations, and head to the lower level. There's many more green Wisps to absorb, so long as you take out the other Lantern Holder creating more dangerous wisps of his own.
